{"tid":371621,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"香港女仔其實不差","createTime":"2017-08-23T19:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T03:24:15.000Z","uid":137977,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f58c01b869ffbc361eddfdbf3ba58eecadce9065","tid":371621,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T19:54:29.000Z","msg":"我的夢想是成為擁有一個島嶼的島主<br />\n我會把她打造成渡假勝地<br />\n有水上樂園，特色小食，天海一色的景觀<br />\n然後讓我認識的朋友在島嶼上生活<br />\n每一天行在沙灘上也能看到熟悉的臉孔<br />\n一直生活下去 即使到了最後的人生<br />\n可以一起坐在茶樓談天說地 回憶舊時<br />\n那一天 有我們的扶持 縱使心裡心痛不捨<br />\n也會穩穩的把你送到我們將來的家<br />\n約定於明年 我們會再見<br />\n六十年後 我們依然會談談天 說說地"},{"pid":"f70fc419c83705761df55b34b89079052be9236f","tid":371621,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adbc43642f836c0852433e19bc0b2e08dc919052","tid":371621,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:30:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c37e59fa90c8554133085fccef0c566badcdb9e7","tid":371621,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:32:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f24b11855442d9f0e51eda489cc28694cdd9e5f5","tid":371621,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:33:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ea234a9637d9e01d85b4bd223894a8142b1f2b8","tid":371621,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:38:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ec44ac6497ee6c63ab89fcbbe8d014453e9c6b4","tid":371621,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:41:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aeeb8df144695872bdee994a0d1fa3019f6f09b1","tid":371621,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}